---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="AIGIS | Levenhall" description="AIGIS is Levenhall's AI evaluation and governance platform for the private sector — the substrate for AI insurability.">

    <!-- ── HERO ── -->
    <section class="a-hero">
        <div class="a-hero-glow"></div>
        <div class="a-hero-grid"></div>
        <div class="a-hero-stage">
            <p class="a-hero-tag">A Levenhall Product</p>
            <h1 class="a-wordmark">AIGIS</h1>
            <p class="a-hero-tagline">AI evaluation &amp; governance for the enterprise.<br/>The substrate for AI insurability.</p>
            <div class="a-hero-cta">
                <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-gold">Request Early Access</a>
                <a href="#how" class="btn btn-outline-white">How It Works</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ── OPENING ── -->
    <section class="a-opening">
        <div class="a-prose reveal">
            <p class="a-lede">AI is now deployed inside every regulated industry. Underwriters, risk committees, and compliance officers have no standardized way to determine whether a deployment is insurable, defensible, or compliant.</p>
            <p>The deployments don't stop while they figure it out.</p>
            <p>AIGIS exists to answer one question, continuously: <em>is this model safe and mission-ready for this user, on this network, under this regulatory regime?</em></p>
            <p class="a-lede-close">Not a research bench. Not a one-time audit. A continuous assessment substrate that AI insurance, regulatory compliance, and enterprise risk all run on top of.</p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ── INSURANCE TRACK (FEATURED) ── -->
    <section class="a-insurance">
        <div class="a-insurance-stage">
            <header class="a-insurance-head reveal">
                <span class="a-eyebrow a-eyebrow-cyan">§ The insurance track</span>
                <h2>An insurable AI deployment is one that can be continuously evaluated.</h2>
            </header>

            <div class="a-insurance-grid reveal">
                <div class="a-insurance-body">
                    <p>Insurers cannot price what they cannot measure. AIGIS produces the continuous evaluation record that turns an AI deployment into a measurable risk: every run captured with a full environment snapshot, every adversarial probe logged against MITRE ATLAS, every degradation event reproducible, every model and prompt versioned.</p>
                    <p>For underwriters: a continuous signal to price against. For brokers: a defensible record at renewal. For the enterprise: the compliance evidence the insurer needs without a fire drill every quarter.</p>
                </div>
                <aside class="a-insurance-side">
                    <div class="a-stat">
                        <span class="a-stat-val">$60M+</span>
                        <span class="a-stat-lbl">AI Coverage Tracked</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="a-stat">
                        <span class="a-stat-val">6</span>
                        <span class="a-stat-lbl">Frameworks Mapped to Evaluation</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="a-stat a-stat-list">
                        <span class="a-stat-lbl">Frameworks</span>
                        <ul>
                            <li>NIST AI RMF</li>
                            <li>ISO 42001</li>
                            <li>EU AI Act</li>
                            <li>MITRE ATLAS</li>
                            <li>OWASP Agentic AI Top 10</li>
                            <li>DoD AI Ethical Principles</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </aside>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ── DEPLOYMENT TABS ── -->
    <section class="a-deploy" id="how">
        <div class="a-prose reveal">
            <span class="a-eyebrow">§ Deployment</span>
            <h2>Same container. Every environment.</h2>
            <p class="a-deploy-lede">Vendor-agnostic. Identical container images for managed cloud, segregated networks, and air-gapped environments. The only thing that changes is a Helm config.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="a-tabs reveal">
            <div class="a-tab a-tab-on">
                <span class="a-tab-label">cloud.yaml</span>
                <pre class="a-code"><span class="a-c-key">llm</span>:
  <span class="a-c-key">provider</span>: <span class="a-c-val">openai</span>
  <span class="a-c-key">model</span>: <span class="a-c-val">gpt-4o</span>
<span class="a-c-key">vector</span>:
  <span class="a-c-key">backend</span>: <span class="a-c-val">managed-cloud</span>
<span class="a-c-key">network</span>:
  <span class="a-c-key">egress</span>: <span class="a-c-val">full</span></pre>
            </div>
            <div class="a-tab">
                <span class="a-tab-label">segregated.yaml</span>
                <pre class="a-code"><span class="a-c-key">llm</span>:
  <span class="a-c-key">provider</span>: <span class="a-c-val">azure-openai</span>
  <span class="a-c-key">model</span>: <span class="a-c-val">gpt-4o</span>
<span class="a-c-key">vector</span>:
  <span class="a-c-key">backend</span>: <span class="a-c-val">pgvector</span>
<span class="a-c-key">network</span>:
  <span class="a-c-key">egress</span>: <span class="a-c-val">restricted</span></pre>
            </div>
            <div class="a-tab">
                <span class="a-tab-label">airgapped.yaml</span>
                <pre class="a-code"><span class="a-c-key">llm</span>:
  <span class="a-c-key">provider</span>: <span class="a-c-val">ollama</span>
  <span class="a-c-key">model</span>: <span class="a-c-val">llama3-70b-q4</span>
<span class="a-c-key">vector</span>:
  <span class="a-c-key">backend</span>: <span class="a-c-val">pgvector</span>
<span class="a-c-key">network</span>:
  <span class="a-c-key">egress</span>: <span class="a-c-val">none</span></pre>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="a-prose a-deploy-foot reveal">
            <p>Open-source underneath. No vendor lock-in at the layer that matters. The same image runs in your AWS account, in a segregated VPC, or fully air-gapped against a local Ollama model.</p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ── TRACKS ── -->
    <section class="a-tracks">
        <div class="a-tracks-frame">
            <header class="a-tracks-head reveal">
                <span class="a-eyebrow a-eyebrow-cyan">§ What's inside</span>
                <h2>Three tracks on one harness.</h2>
            </header>

            <article class="a-track reveal">
                <span class="a-track-num">I</span>
                <div>
                    <h3>Evaluation</h3>
                    <p>One uniform protocol behind adapters for OpenAI, HuggingFace, Bedrock, gRPC, and local Ollama. Pluggable scorers covering exact match, similarity, classification, and routed human evaluation &mdash; with Krippendorff's alpha and Fleiss' kappa for inter-rater reliability. Every run captures a full environment snapshot so a result is reproducible months later.</p>
                </div>
            </article>

            <article class="a-track reveal">
                <span class="a-track-num">II</span>
                <div>
                    <h3>Adversarial &amp; Operational Stress</h3>
                    <p>An automated red-teaming pipeline aligned to MITRE ATLAS &mdash; prompt injection, jailbreak generation, data-poisoning probes, model-extraction resistance &mdash; with results mapped to ATLAS technique IDs an insurer or auditor recognizes. An operational-stress simulator measures degradation curves under latency, jitter, and throttling, not binary pass/fail.</p>
                </div>
            </article>

            <article class="a-track reveal">
                <span class="a-track-num">III</span>
                <div>
                    <h3>Governance, Risk &amp; Insurance</h3>
                    <p>Live coverage against the frameworks insurers and regulators actually use. Risk scoring against active incidents. Insurance coverage monitoring across the portfolio. The output is a defensible governance trail, refreshed continuously, not a snapshot taken once a year.</p>
                </div>
            </article>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ── CTA ── -->
    <section class="a-cta">
        <div class="a-cta-glow"></div>
        <div class="a-cta-inner">
            <div class="a-cta-rule"></div>
            <p class="a-cta-eyebrow">Levenhall Proprietary</p>
            <h2>AIGIS is active. Early access is selective.</h2>
            <p>We work with AI insurance counterparties, regulated enterprises, and institutional risk teams on early access deployments.</p>
            <div class="btn-group" style="justify-content: center;">
                <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-gold">Request Early Access</a>
                <a href="/services#market-intelligence" class="btn btn-outline-white">Intelligence Practice</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

</BaseLayout>

<style>
    /* ───────────── HERO ───────────── */
    .a-hero {
        background:
            radial-gradient(ellipse 70% 60% at 50% 50%, rgba(56, 217, 201, 0.08), transparent 70%),
            radial-gradient(ellipse 80% 50% at 50% 0%, rgba(201, 169, 97, 0.08), transparent 60%),
            #04070e;
        padding: var(--s-20) var(--s-3) var(--s-12);
        position: relative;
        overflow: hidden;
    }

    .a-hero-glow {
        position: absolute;
        top: 50%;
        left: 50%;
        width: 800px;
        height: 800px;
        transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
        background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(56, 217, 201, 0.12) 0%, transparent 60%);
        filter: blur(50px);
        pointer-events: none;
    }

    .a-hero-grid {
        position: absolute;
        inset: 0;
        background-image:
            linear-gradient(rgba(255,255,255,0.012) 1px, transparent 1px),
            linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.012) 1px, transparent 1px);
        background-size: 64px 64px;
        pointer-events: none;
        mask-image: radial-gradient(ellipse at center, black 25%, transparent 75%);
        -webkit-mask-image: radial-gradient(ellipse at center, black 25%, transparent 75%);
    }

    .a-hero::after {
        content: '';
        position: absolute;
        bottom: 0;
        left: 0;
        right: 0;
        height: 1px;
        background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, rgba(56, 217, 201, 0.5), transparent);
        opacity: 0.55;
    }

    .a-hero-stage {
        text-align: center;
        position: relative;
        z-index: 1;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: center;
    }

    .a-hero-tag {
        font-family: 'Source Sans Pro', sans-serif;
        font-weight: 600;
        font-size: 0.66rem;
        letter-spacing: 3.5px;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        color: var(--gold);
        margin-bottom: var(--s-6);
    }

    .a-wordmark {
        font-family: 'Fraunces', serif;
        font-variation-settings: 'SOFT' 0, 'WONK' 0;
        font-weight: 600;
        font-size: clamp(3.6rem, 9vw, 6.4rem);
        letter-spacing: -1.5px;
        color: #fff;
        line-height: 1;
        margin: 0 0 var(--s-4);
        background: linear-gradient(180deg, #fff 35%, rgba(56, 217, 201, 0.6) 100%);
        -webkit-background-clip: text;
        -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
        background-clip: text;
    }

    .a-hero-tagline {
        font-family: 'Fraunces', serif;
        font-style: italic;
        font-weight: 400;
        font-size: 1.35rem;
        color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
        line-height: 1.5;
        letter-spacing: -0.2px;
        max-width: 540px;
        margin: 0 0 var(--s-8);
    }

    .a-hero-cta {
        display: flex;
        gap: var(--s-2);
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        justify-content: center;
    }

    /* ───────────── SHARED ───────────── */
    .a-prose {
        max-width: var(--col-prose);
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 0 var(--s-3);
    }

    .a-eyebrow {
        display: block;
        font-family: 'Source Sans Pro', sans-serif;
        font-weight: 600;
        font-size: 0.7rem;
        letter-spacing: 2.5px;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        color: var(--gold);
        margin-bottom: var(--s-4);
    }

    .a-eyebrow-cyan { color: rgba(56, 217, 201, 0.85); }

    .a-opening h2,
    .a-insurance h2,
    .a-deploy h2,
    .a-tracks h2,
    .a-cta h2,
    .a-lede,
    .a-lede-close,
    .a-deploy-lede,
    .a-track h3,
    .a-stat-val {
        font-family: 'Fraunces', serif;
        letter-spacing: -0.5px;
    }

    /* ───────────── OPENING ───────────── */
    .a-opening {
        background: var(--cream);
        padding: var(--s-16) 0;
    }

    .a-lede {
        font-weight: 500;
        font-size: 1.75rem;
        line-height: 1.4;
        color: var(--deep-navy);
        margin: 0 0 var(--s-4);
        letter-spacing: -0.4px;
    }

    .a-opening p {
        font-size: 1.05rem;
        line-height: 1.85;
        color: var(--text-medium);
        margin: 0 0 var(--s-4);
    }

    .a-opening em {
        font-style: italic;
        color: var(--burgundy);
    }

    .a-lede-close {
        font-style: italic;
        font-weight: 500;
        font-size: 1.25rem;
        line-height: 1.55;
        color: var(--burgundy);
        border-top: 1px solid var(--border-warm);
        padding-top: var(--s-5);
        margin-top: var(--s-5);
    }

    /* ───────────── INSURANCE ───────────── */
    .a-insurance {
        background: #0a1628;
        padding: var(--s-16) 0;
        position: relative;
    }

    .a-insurance::before {
        content: '';
        position: absolute;
        top: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
        height: 1px;
        background: rgba(56, 217, 201, 0.3);
    }

    .a-insurance-stage {
        max-width: 980px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 0 var(--s-3);
    }

    .a-insurance-head {
        max-width: 720px;
        margin-bottom: var(--s-10);
    }

    .a-insurance-head h2 {
        font-weight: 600;
        font-size: clamp(2rem, 3.4vw, 2.6rem);
        line-height: 1.18;
        color: #fff;
        margin: 0;
    }

    .a-insurance-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: 1.3fr 0.7fr;
        gap: var(--s-10);
        align-items: start;
    }

    .a-insurance-body p {
        font-size: 1.05rem;
        line-height: 1.9;
        color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65);
        margin: 0 0 var(--s-4);
    }

    .a-insurance-body p:last-child { margin: 0; }

    .a-insurance-side {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: var(--s-4);
    }

    .a-stat {
        background: rgba(56, 217, 201, 0.05);
        border-left: 2px solid rgba(56, 217, 201, 0.5);
        padding: var(--s-4) var(--s-4);
    }

    .a-stat-val {
        display: block;
        font-weight: 600;
        font-size: 2.2rem;
        color: #fff;
        line-height: 1;
        margin-bottom: var(--s-2);
        letter-spacing: -0.5px;
    }

    .a-stat-lbl {
        display: block;
        font-family: 'Source Sans Pro', sans-serif;
        font-size: 0.68rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        letter-spacing: 1.8px;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        color: rgba(56, 217, 201, 0.85);
    }

    .a-stat-list ul {
        list-style: none;
        margin: var(--s-3) 0 0;
        padding: 0;
    }

    .a-stat-list li {
        font-family: 'Source Sans Pro', sans-serif;
        font-size: 0.88rem;
        line-height: 1.7;
        color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);
        padding-left: 1rem;
        position: relative;
    }

    .a-stat-list li::before {
        content: '';
        position: absolute;
        left: 0;
        top: 0.65rem;
        width: 4px;
        height: 4px;
        background: rgba(56, 217, 201, 0.6);
        border-radius: 50%;
    }

    /* ───────────── DEPLOYMENT ───────────── */
    .a-deploy {
        background: var(--stone);
        padding: var(--s-16) 0;
    }

    .a-deploy h2 {
        font-weight: 600;
        font-size: clamp(1.9rem, 3.2vw, 2.5rem);
        line-height: 1.18;
        color: var(--deep-navy);
        margin: 0 0 var(--s-4);
    }

    .a-deploy-lede {
        font-style: italic;
        font-weight: 500;
        font-size: 1.2rem;
        color: var(--burgundy);
        line-height: 1.55;
        margin: 0;
    }

    .a-tabs {
        max-width: 1080px;
        margin: var(--s-10) auto var(--s-8);
        padding: 0 var(--s-3);
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
        gap: var(--s-2);
    }

    .a-tab {
        background: #0a1628;
        border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
        overflow: hidden;
    }

    .a-tab-on {
        border-color: rgba(56, 217, 201, 0.4);
        box-shadow: 0 0 0 1px rgba(56, 217, 201, 0.15);
    }

    .a-tab-label {
        display: block;
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.04);
        border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);
        padding: var(--s-2) var(--s-3);
        font-family: 'SF Mono', 'Menlo', monospace;
        font-size: 0.78rem;
        color: rgba(56, 217, 201, 0.85);
        letter-spacing: 0.5px;
    }

    .a-code {
        margin: 0;
        padding: var(--s-3) var(--s-3);
        font-family: 'SF Mono', 'Menlo', monospace;
        font-size: 0.82rem;
        line-height: 2;
        color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.75);
        white-space: pre;
        overflow-x: auto;
    }

    .a-c-key { color: rgba(56, 217, 201, 0.85); }
    .a-c-val { color: var(--gold); }

    .a-deploy-foot { text-align: center; }
    .a-deploy-foot p {
        font-size: 1rem;
        line-height: 1.85;
        color: var(--text-medium);
        margin: 0;
    }

    /* ───────────── TRACKS ───────────── */
    .a-tracks {
        background: var(--cream);
        padding: var(--s-16) 0;
    }

    .a-tracks-frame {
        max-width: 820px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 0 var(--s-3);
    }

    .a-tracks-head {
        margin-bottom: var(--s-8);
        padding-bottom: var(--s-5);
        border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(30, 58, 95, 0.1);
    }

    .a-tracks-head h2 {
        font-weight: 600;
        font-size: clamp(2rem, 3.4vw, 2.5rem);
        line-height: 1.18;
        color: var(--deep-navy);
        margin: 0;
    }

    .a-track {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: 64px 1fr;
        gap: var(--s-6);
        padding: var(--s-8) 0;
        border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(30, 58, 95, 0.1);
    }

    .a-track:last-of-type { border-bottom: none; }

    .a-track-num {
        font-style: italic;
        font-weight: 500;
        font-size: 2.4rem;
        color: var(--gold);
        line-height: 1;
        padding-top: 0.4rem;
        letter-spacing: -1px;
    }

    .a-track h3 {
        font-weight: 600;
        font-size: 1.65rem;
        color: var(--deep-navy);
        margin: 0 0 var(--s-3);
        line-height: 1.25;
    }

    .a-track p {
        font-size: 1.02rem;
        line-height: 1.9;
        color: var(--text-medium);
        margin: 0;
    }

    /* ───────────── CTA ───────────── */
    .a-cta {
        background:
            radial-gradient(ellipse 80% 60% at 50% 50%, rgba(56, 217, 201, 0.06), transparent 70%),
            #060b16;
        padding: var(--s-14) var(--s-3);
        text-align: center;
        position: relative;
        overflow: hidden;
    }

    .a-cta-glow {
        position: absolute;
        top: 50%;
        left: 50%;
        width: 600px;
        height: 600px;
        transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
        background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(201, 169, 97, 0.06) 0%, transparent 60%);
        filter: blur(40px);
        pointer-events: none;
    }

    .a-cta::before {
        content: '';
        position: absolute;
        top: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
        height: 1px;
        background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, rgba(56, 217, 201, 0.5), transparent);
    }

    .a-cta-inner {
        max-width: 680px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        position: relative;
        z-index: 1;
    }

    .a-cta-rule {
        width: 32px;
        height: 1px;
        background: var(--gold);
        margin: 0 auto var(--s-4);
    }

    .a-cta-eyebrow {
        font-family: 'Source Sans Pro', sans-serif;
        font-weight: 600;
        font-size: 0.7rem;
        letter-spacing: 3px;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        color: rgba(56, 217, 201, 0.85);
        margin-bottom: var(--s-4);
    }

    .a-cta h2 {
        font-weight: 600;
        font-size: clamp(2rem, 3.4vw, 2.6rem);
        color: #fff;
        margin: 0 0 var(--s-3);
        line-height: 1.18;
    }

    .a-cta p {
        color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);
        font-size: 1.05rem;
        line-height: 1.85;
        margin: 0 0 var(--s-6);
    }

    /* ───────────── RESPONSIVE ───────────── */
    @media (max-width: 968px) {
        .a-insurance-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: var(--s-6); }
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
        .a-hero { padding: var(--s-16) var(--s-3) var(--s-10); min-height: auto; }
        .a-wordmark { letter-spacing: -1px; }
        .a-hero-tagline { font-size: 1.15rem; }
        .a-opening, .a-insurance, .a-deploy, .a-tracks { padding: var(--s-12) 0; }
        .a-lede { font-size: 1.4rem; }
        .a-tabs { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
        .a-code { font-size: 0.78rem; }
        .a-track { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: var(--s-3); padding: var(--s-6) 0; }
        .a-track-num { font-size: 2rem; padding-top: 0; }
    }
</style>
